            <title>[LUDOC-64] Change debugfs information to use FID lookup</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-64</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Bug opened to track manual update from &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1162&quot; title=&quot;debugfs 1.41.90.wc3 not printing path on mdt&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-1162&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-1162&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&quot;For the second step, where you are looking up the FID on the MDS, you should instead be using &quot;lfs fid2path &lt;/p&gt;
{FID}
